## The Full Rainbow: Classic Pride Nails That Never Miss

Classic rainbow pride nails have never been a safe choice  they have always been a statement. The six-colour <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pride_flag' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>rainbow flag</a> (red, orange, yellow, green, blue, violet) translates to nails in more ways than most people explore. Skittle nails  one colour per finger  are the original and still the cleanest execution. Ombre rainbow gradients blend all six across a single nail or across the full set. Holographic rainbow polish catches every colour in the spectrum in a single coat, for the person who wants rainbow without the precision work. For the full rainbow edit, our <a href='/blog/rainbow-nails-pride'>rainbow nails pride guide</a> goes deeper on every variation.

